5. Parser extracts gesture, emits: `{ type: 'gesture', data: { pattern: 'flickers between violet and grey' }}`
6. Orb transitions to flickering animation
7. Luna finishes with: `*settles into a confident, steady glow*`
8. Orb transitions to steady idle state

